erate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/74379/', '', 'Diamorphine, Acamprosate, Lofexidine, Naltrexone, Varenicline, Disulfiram, Nalmefene, Nicotine, Codeine, Naltrexone, Oxymorphone, More', 'Tolvaptan', 1767369485);
